snippet.title: Hanno - Teaser
snippet.description:
You can now wishlist Hanno on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2851120/Hanno/

Follow our newsletter: https://www.onewayeleven.com

Join Hanno, an unusual elephant, and Vimal, his newly young companion, as they face challenges brought by…fate? Fight, stealth, explore, sort things out and get ready to uncover the cost of loyalty in this stunning, mysterious, heartfelt third-person action-adventure game.
